&lt;div&gt;If you have questions, please call 512-336-4368 and leave a message or you may send an email to &lt;a href="mailto:celebraterecovery@hcbc.com"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;celebraterecovery@hcbc.com&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Women are invited to travel with us to the island of Lesvos, Greece - and serve at a community center, which was established in response to the lack of shower and laundry facilities for the women and children living in the refugee camp. The Center - intended to be a loving and hospitable environment - provides warm showers, a baby bath area, a laundry facility, a food bank, and much more.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;March 24th-April 2nd (registration closes December 12th)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

